title: Trade setup for November 21: Top 15 things to know before the opening bells
description: Given the strengthening momentum, experts expect the Nifty 50 to touch its record high of 26,277 soon, provided it holds 26,100 as an immediate support. Beyond this, 26,500 is the level to watch, while the sacrosanct support is placed at 25,800.
